page.title: 08POPULATION
page.content: There are several old gravestones dating from the 17th century. Some have only initials e.g. H.C. 1637 and J.C. 1656 also E.B. September 6. 1672 There are some full names RICARDUS THISTLET 1657. JAMES HOBB WAS BIRIED THE FIRST OF MAY 1666. There are gravestones dating from 1700 to about 1920.The oldest person buried here is HENRIETTA COLE DIED 1875 AGED 91.There are several graves of babies buried in the 19th century. ELIZA MATTHEWS DIED 1890 AGED SEVEN MONTHS. There are somefamily groups all buried in one grave. SWINSCOE 1859. There is a large memorial to the dead of the two World Wars.
